  {
    "type": "EXEGETICAL (ORIGINAL LANGUAGES)",
    "name": "Keil and Delitzsch Biblical Commentary on the Old Testament",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Jacob's Departure from his Parents' House. - Rebekah's complaint reminded Isaac of his own call, and his consequent duty to provide for Jacob's marriage in a manner corresponding to the divine counsels of salvation.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Genesis 28:1-5",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Genesis 28:1-5",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "He called Jacob, therefore, and sent him to Padan-Aram to his mother's relations, with instructions to seek a wife there, and not among the daughters of Canaan, giving him at the same time the \"blessing of Abraham,\" i.e., the blessing of promise, which Abraham had repeatedly received from the Lord, but which is more especially recorded in Genesis 17:2., and Genesis 22:16-18.",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "He called Jacob, therefore, and sent him to Padan-Aram to his mother's relations, with instructions to seek a wife there, and not among the daughters of Canaan, giving him at the same time the \"blessing of Abraham,\" i.e., the blessing of promise, which Abraham had repeatedly received from the Lord, but which is more especially recorded in ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Genesis 17:2",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "., and ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Genesis 22:16-18",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
